# SPEC-035-4-03 §Goldens directory.
#
# Pixel-perfect golden PNGs for the `/design-system` visual regression
# suite live alongside this file. Bootstrap the directory by running
# `npm run gen:visual-goldens` locally; commit the 21 generated PNGs
# (`design-system-full.png` + `design-system-card-{01..20}.png`).
#
# If `du -sb tests/visual-regression/goldens/` exceeds 512000 bytes,
# track the directory under git-lfs:
#   git lfs track "tests/visual-regression/goldens/*.png"
# and re-stage the goldens. SPEC-035-4-04's
# `scripts/ci/check-goldens-size.sh` enforces the threshold in CI.
